high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn left go to the counter, turn right
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left to the counter
Cut the apple on the counter
Move to the left to the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Move a bit to the right
Take an apple piece from the counter
Move to the left to the sink
Put the apple piece in the sink, wash the apple piece with water, pick up the apple piece from the sink
Turn around, go to the fridge
Put the apple piece in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Wash a piece of apple and cool it

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Step to the left to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Wash the apple piece in the sink and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the piece of apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To wash a piece of apple plus place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right, then left and face the counter on your right.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Face the counter on your left.
Slice the apple in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn right then face the apple on the counter to your left.
Take an apple slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink to your right.
Wash the apple in the sink in front of you then take it out.
Turn around and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the apple in the fridge in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean apple slice in the fridge.
